      "writtenOn": "2020-04-24T15:20:22Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "The TODO is misplaced. It’s just a comment right now, so the behavior isn’t incorrect, but it seems misleading for the future version of this code that will forward exceptions.\n\nWe will want to forward exceptions to original_handlers_, even if we see an exception for a task that isn’t mach_task_self(). Just because we’re unprepared to deal with exceptions for child processes doesn’t mean that the previous handler was also unprepared.",
