      "message": "This doesn’t belong in namespace crashpad.\n\nIn fact, it’s only used in ExceptionSnapshotIOS::InitializeFromMachException. So it doesn’t belong in crashpad::internal or an unnamed namespace either. It belongs in-line in the only function that uses it.",
