      "writtenOn": "2020-04-24T15:20:22Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "You’re not 100% sure of the flavor you received. Part of InitializeCPUContextX86_64’s job is to figure it out. The exception handler was invoked with a flavor, and you have it available to you in the flavor argument, which you should use here.",
      "revId": "362968ada558c3419190362d4fef9cad0e27b939",
